                    Python <span class="accent">·</span> 
                    Juniper <span class="accent">·</span> 
                    Linux <span class="accent">·</span> 
                    React <span class="accent">·</span> 
                    Proxmox <span class="accent">·</span> 
                    NETCONF <span class="accent">·</span> 
                    PyEZ <span class="accent">·</span> Git
                </p>
